    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were all, believe me, every one of us was on board.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And it was just the most magnificent sight to have seen the Statue of Liberty approaching-- as we approached it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And to this day, when I cross that Verrazano Bridge I strain to see the statue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "It has enormous meaning for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And I just have a-- a wonderful, beautiful feeling inside whenever I see it, and it is just enormously meaningful.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
